room_title: Escape room "Quake Escape" by Confundrum Escape Rooms in Idaho Falls
room_address: 763 S Woodruff Ave, Idaho Falls, ID 83404
room_description: While having dinner at a Mexican Cantina restaurant you find yourself in the middle of an earthquake. The main entrance is inaccessible and you find yourself trapped. The staff, like Elvis, have left the building and you are on your own. Concerned that the building may crumble down around you, instincts kick and you start searching for an alternative way out so you can check on family and loved ones. Will you survive and make your escape or will your family list you as missing with the rest of the area victims? Enjoy our Escape Room Puzzles in this amazing Escape Rooms.
